<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT78">
<l>kaṇṭu vaṇaṅkiṉārk keṉṉāṅkoṟ kāmaṉuṭaṟ</l>
<l>koṇṭa tavattāṟ kumaiyuṇartta vaṇṭalampun</l>
<l>tāralaṅkal nīṇmuṭiyāṉ ṟaṉpeyarē kēṭṭirun taṅ</l>
<l>kāralaṅka lāṉamaiyā lāyntu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As Umā instructed the ascetic [Śiva] who struck Kāma’s body,</l>
<l>[he] kept listening to the names of [the Lord] with a long crown</l>
<l>[adorned with] a flower garland swarmed by bees and was fully moved there.</l>
<l>[If we] examine [this]: what will happen to those who have seen and worshipped</l>
<l rend="indent">[Him directly]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
